<HEAD>Swiss Journalist Killed in Desert Accident</HEAD>
<DATELINE>PARIS (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A vehicle carrying a Swiss TV crew toppled down a
sand dune in northern Chad, killing a journalist and injuring five
other people, the Chadian Embassy reported Monday.
