<HEAD>Rebels Claim Victory Over Government Troops</HEAD>
<DATELINE>KHARTOUM, Sudan (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Rebels in northern Ethiopia on Monday
claimed they destroyed two government army brigades, killing and
wounding more than a thousand troops.
