<HEAD>Stage Collapses During Concert, 55 People Injured</HEAD>
<DATELINE>RIO DE JANEIRO, Brazil (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Part of the stage collapsed at the
beginning of an inaugural concert at a theater in southeastern
Brazil, injuring 55 musicians.
